---
import Typewriter from './copy/typewriter.astro';
---

<section class="services reveal" id="services">
    <div class="services__header">
        <p class="services__overline">
            <span class="services__overline-plain">How I create </span><span class="services__overline-accent">leverage</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="services__headline">How I Create Leverage</h2>
        <p class="services__description">I step in where product, technology, and execution start to pull apart — helping companies regain clarity, structure, and forward momentum.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__flow">

    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="services__step stagger stagger-1">
        <div class="services__step-marker">
            <span class="services__step-number">01</span>
            <span class="services__step-line"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="services__step-content">
            <p class="services__step-label">Recognize</p>
            <h3 class="services__when-title">When I step in</h3>
            <p class="services__when-intro">I work with companies when product, technology, and execution need stronger direction, better structure, and clearer ownership.</p>

            <div class="services__accordion">
            <details class="services__accordion-item">
                <summary class="services__accordion-summary">You need technical leadership before a full-time CTO makes sense</summary>
                <p class="services__accordion-body">When product development is moving, but technical decisions still depend too heavily on founders, managers, or individual developers. I step in to create direction, establish ownership, and turn technical uncertainty into structured execution.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="services__accordion-item">
                <summary class="services__accordion-summary">Product, engineering, and business priorities are no longer aligned</summary>
                <p class="services__accordion-body">When teams are working hard, but progress slows down because priorities conflict, decisions drift, and execution creates rework. I help reconnect business goals, technical decisions, and delivery focus so momentum becomes measurable again.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="services__accordion-item">
                <summary class="services__accordion-summary">Your team delivers, but the current setup will not scale</summary>
                <p class="services__accordion-body">When delivery depends on improvisation, key people carry too much context, and growth starts creating friction instead of leverage. I help build the structures, workflows, and decision paths that allow teams to move faster without creating more chaos.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="services__accordion-item">
                <summary class="services__accordion-summary">You need clarity before committing to the next phase</summary>
                <p class="services__accordion-body">When the pressure is real, the next step matters, and nobody has yet turned the situation into a workable plan. I help define priorities, surface trade-offs, and create an execution path that is realistic, actionable, and aligned with the business.</p>
            </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="services__step stagger stagger-1">
        <div class="services__step-marker">
            <span class="services__step-number">02</span>
            <span class="services__step-line"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="services__step-content">
            <p class="services__step-label">Solve</p>
            <h3 class="services__step-title">What I deliver</h3>
            <p class="services__step-intro">Structured support across three areas — from strategic clarity to hands-on execution to scalable operations.</p>

    <div class="services__pane">
        <div class="services__section">
            <div class="services__section-header">
                <span class="services__section-number services__section-number--terracotta">01</span>
                <h3 class="services__section-title">Direction & Decisions</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="services__section-description">For founders and leadership teams who need technical clarity before committing to a direction.</p>
            <ul class="services__section-bullets">
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-terracotta);">Technical due diligence</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-terracotta);">Architecture assessment</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-terracotta);">Build vs. buy evaluation</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-terracotta);">Roadmap review</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="services__section-ideal">Ideal for: pre-investment, pivot decisions, scaling plans</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="services__divider" />

        <div class="services__section">
            <div class="services__section-header">
                <span class="services__section-number services__section-number--teal">02</span>
                <h3 class="services__section-title">Delivery & Engineering</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="services__section-description">For teams that need hands-on leadership to move product work forward with more focus, speed, and execution discipline.</p>
            <ul class="services__section-bullets">
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-teal);">Product and engineering leadership</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-teal);">Sprint planning and delivery</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-teal);">Team setup and mentoring</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-teal);">Full-stack implementation support</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="services__section-ideal">Ideal for: MVPs, rebuilds, delivery bottlenecks</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="services__divider" />

        <div class="services__section">
            <div class="services__section-header">
                <span class="services__section-number services__section-number--sage">03</span>
                <h3 class="services__section-title">Systems & Operations</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="services__section-description">For growing companies that need stronger structures, clearer processes, and technical operations that can support scale.</p>
            <ul class="services__section-bullets">
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-sage);">Engineering process design</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-sage);">Hiring and onboarding</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-sage);">Performance monitoring</li>
                <li style="--accent: var(--clr-sage);">Incident management</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="services__section-ideal">Ideal for: scaling teams, post-launch growth, operational complexity</p>
        </div>
    </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="services__step stagger stagger-1">
        <div class="services__step-marker">
            <span class="services__step-number">03</span>
        </div>
        <div class="services__step-content">
            <p class="services__step-label">Engage</p>
            <h3 class="services__step-title">How we work together</h3>
            <p class="services__step-intro">Choose the engagement model that fits your situation — from focused advisory to ongoing technical leadership.</p>

            <div class="services__plans">
                <div class="services__plan">
                    <div class="services__plan-left">
                        <h4 class="services__plan-title">On-Demand Advisory & Engineering</h4>
                        <p class="services__plan-desc">Flexible senior support for strategy, architecture, technical reviews, and focused execution — when you need experienced input without committing to a larger engagement.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="services__plan-price-row">
                        <span class="services__plan-price-from">from</span>
                        <span class="services__plan-price">$130</span>
                        <span class="services__plan-price-unit">/ hour</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="services__plan services__plan--highlighted">
                    <div class="services__plan-left">
                        <h4 class="services__plan-title">Focused 2-Week Cycle</h4>
                        <p class="services__plan-desc">A structured two-week engagement for hands-on product work, delivery support, and clearly scoped progress across a focused initiative.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="services__plan-price-row">
                        <span class="services__plan-price-from">from</span>
                        <span class="services__plan-price">$4,999</span>
                        <span class="services__plan-price-unit">/ cycle</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="services__plan">
                    <div class="services__plan-left">
                        <h4 class="services__plan-title">Technical Leadership Retainer</h4>
                        <p class="services__plan-desc">Ongoing technical leadership, architectural guidance, and senior continuity for teams that need experienced support across product and engineering.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="services__plan-right">
                        <div class="services__plan-price-row">
                            <span class="services__plan-price-from">from</span>
                            <span class="services__plan-price">$2,499</span>
                            <span class="services__plan-price-unit">/ month</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="services__plan-note">Minimum engagement: 6 months.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="services__cta">
                <p class="services__cta-text">Not sure which fits? Let's talk.</p>
                <a class="services__cta-button" href="#contact">Book a Discovery Call</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    </div><!-- /.services__flow -->
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .services {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 80px 144px 64px;

        &__header {
            max-width: 560px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        &__overline {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
        }

        &__overline-plain {
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
        }

        &__overline-accent {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--clr-teal);
        }

        &__headline {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 6rem;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            line-height: 0.95;
        }

        &__description {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.4375rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.7);
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        /* Narrative flow */
        &__flow {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0;
        }

        &__step {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        &__step-marker {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 40px;
        }

        &__step-number {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--clr-terracotta);
            line-height: 1;
        }

        &__step-line {
            flex: 1;
            width: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--clr-terracotta), transparent);
            margin-top: 12px;
            min-height: 40px;
        }

        &__step-label {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--clr-terracotta);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        &__step-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        &__step-title {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        &__step-intro {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1875rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.65);
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 560px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* When I step in */
        &__when-title {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        &__when-intro {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1875rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.65);
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 560px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        &__accordion {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-self: stretch;
        }

        &__accordion-item {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border-dark);

            &:last-child {
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border-dark);
            }
        }

        &__accordion-summary {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            padding: 1.25rem 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;

            &::-webkit-details-marker {
                display: none;
            }

            &::after {
                content: '+';
                font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                color: var(--clr-text-muted);
                flex-shrink: 0;
                transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            }
        }

        &__accordion-item[open] > &__accordion-summary::after {
            content: '−';
        }

        &__accordion-body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.65);
            line-height: 1.65;
            padding: 0 0 1.25rem;
            max-width: 640px;
        }

        /* Single pane with three sections */
        &__pane {
            background: var(--clr-bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--clr-border-dark);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0;
        }

        &__section {
            padding: 36px 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
            column-gap: 2.5rem;
            row-gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        &__section-header {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        &__section-number {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1;

            &--terracotta { color: var(--clr-terracotta); }
            &--teal { color: var(--clr-teal); }
            &--sage { color: var(--clr-sage); }
        }

        &__section-title {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        &__section-description {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.3125rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.7);
            line-height: 1.6;
            grid-column: 1;
        }

        &__section-bullets {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            grid-column: 2;
            grid-row: 2 / 4;
            align-self: center;

            li {
                font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.65);
                padding-left: 1rem;
                position: relative;

                &::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 0;
                    top: 50%;
                    transform: translateY(-50%);
                    width: 5px;
                    height: 5px;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    background: var(--accent);
                }
            }
        }

        &__section-ideal {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.45);
            grid-column: 1;
        }

        &__divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border-dark);
            margin: 0 40px;
        }

        &__plans {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        &__plan {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2rem;
            background: var(--clr-bg-surface);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            border: 1px solid var(--clr-border-dark);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 28px 36px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;

            &:hover {
                border-color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.12);
            }

            &--highlighted {
                border-left: 3px solid var(--clr-terracotta);
                padding-left: 33px;
            }
        }

        &__plan-left {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        &__plan-title {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        &__plan-desc {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1875rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.55);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        &__plan-price-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 4px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        &__plan-right {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 6px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        &__plan-note {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.4);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        &__plan-price-from {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.45);
            margin-right: 4px;
        }

        &__plan-price {
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.75rem;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            line-height: 1;
        }

        &__plan-price-unit {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.45);
        }

        &__cta {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        &__cta-text {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        }

        &__cta-button {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-white);
            background-color: var(--clr-bg-surface);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--clr-text-primary);
            border-radius: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            transition:
                background-color 0.2s ease,
                border-color 0.2s ease;

            &:hover {
                background-color: var(--clr-text-primary);
                color: #151310;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1440px) {
        .services {
            padding: 80px 80px 64px;


        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .services {
            padding: 64px 2rem 48px;


            &__step {
                gap: 1.25rem;
            }

            &__step-marker {
                width: 28px;
            }

            &__step-title, &__when-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            &__header {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            &__headline {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }

            &__section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            &__section-bullets {
                grid-column: 1;
                grid-row: auto;
            }

            &__plans-headline {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            &__plan {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 1rem;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .services {
            padding: 64px 1.25rem 48px;

        }
    }
</style>
